 swirls are less\ndistinguishable from their environment. Vortex tubes reaching the corona show a\ncomplex relationship with the coronal emission.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 5 May 2023 18:02:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-09"}
