petitive, while avoiding the massive overhead arising from\nfeature engineering and rule definition needed to adapt to other datasets,\ndifferent entity and relation types, or new domains.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 6 May 2023 07:06:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-09"}
